ore driving into the lane for a layup with 1 second to go, tying it at 16.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"27 seconds\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"the lane\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"a layup\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"1 second\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had seven points for the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9674148995362808, \"rank\": 0.033498285111267706, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"seven points\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hopes the success of the team will lead to more interest in basketball in his country.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"more interest\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"his country\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Before 3x3 basketball, we were never in a position to make it to the Olympics or even make it to a world championship,\\\" de Jong said.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3x3 basketball\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"a world championship\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"de Jong\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1635}]}, {\"s